			<h4>School of Hope Student Sponsorship</h4>
			<p>
				Students in this program come to school each day and then return home to live in the village with their families. Student sponsorship is $35 per month or $420 annually. Your sponsorship funds provide your Haitian student with a quality Christ-centered education. Sponsorship funds go toward:
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor">
				<li>
					Daily nutritious meal
				</li>
				<li>
					Christ-centered curriculum and teacher training
				</li>
				<li>
					School-specific improvement initiatives
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Sponsors can choose a boy or girl student at the Kindergarten, Primary (Elementary) or Secondary (Jr. and Sr. High) grade levels. Once a sponsor is connected with their student, they will receive a profile card with a photo and personal information about their sponsored child. 
			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>What You’ll Receive From Your Child:</strong>
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor">
				<li>Annual photo</li>
				<li>School updates throughout the year</li>
				<li>Reply letters to any correspondence you send to your student </li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				<strong>Ways to Connect With Your Child:</strong>
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor">
				<li>
					Send letters and photographs online
				</li>
				<li>
					Give them a gift through our online store
				</li>
				<li>
					Visit your child in Haiti on a Mission Trip!
				</li>
			</ul>
