			<h4>Village of Hope Orphan Sponsorship</h4>
			<p>Village of Hope children are raised in a Christ-centered, supportive community, giving the children a relational family environment where they can grow and thrive physically, mentally, emotionally, and spiritually. </p>

<p>We have created "family clusters" where each child will have up to 10 sponsors, each donating $50 (heart icon) monthly. A sponsor may choose as many of the $50 increments per month, up to the needed $500 per month to completely fund that child's sponsorship.</p>

<h4><strong>Sponsorship funds are used to provide: </strong></h4>
<ul class="learnSponsor">
<li>Balanced nutrition</li>                                   
<li>Hygiene</li>
<li>Medical needs/general healthcare</li>
<li>Schooling</li>
<li>Tutoring</li>
<li>Housing</li>
<li>Utilities</li>
<li>Maintenance</li>
<li>Security</li>
<li>Transportation</li>
<li>Extra-curricular child development activities </li>
</ul>

